    "assessment_notes": "Assessment (Feb 3, 2026, ~12:00 PM):\nOVERALL RATING: 3/5* (Conditional) - MAYBE\n\nLOCATION:\n- Al-Rahba South - Typical Emirati neighborhood\n- Quiet area with large villas\n- Demographics: 80-90% Emirati population\n- Residential catchment area\n\nFACILITIES STATUS:\n- Tyre repair shop: Currently leased (Hassan Al-Hosani - active tenant)\n- Car wash (left & right): Will be operated by ADNOC (NOT available for rent)\n- Vacuum bay: Will be operated by ADNOC (NOT available for rent)\n- ADNOC Lube (loop): Present on site\n- ADNOC Oasis: Operational convenience store\n- Food trucks: Active F&B presence (Laser Time, Radio Cafe, others)\n\n🔥 CRITICAL UPDATE (Feb 3, 2026 - 12:34 PM):\nTENANT TRANSITION OPPORTUNITY\n\nCurrent Situation (via Lav Kumar, ADNOC - WhatsApp):\n- Current tenant: Hassan Al-Hosani (tyre repair)\n- **Being asked to leave by June 30, 2026**\n- Current rent: ~120,000 AED per year\n- **ADNOC wants MORE RENT**\n- **ADNOC wants BETTER BRAND**\n\nStrategic Implications:\n- Site becomes available June 30, 2026\n- ADNOC actively seeking brand upgrade\n- ExpressFit could position as premium replacement\n- 6-month timeline for planning/negotiation\n- Rent baseline: 120,000 AED (ADNOC seeking higher)\n\nContact: Lav Kumar (ADNOC) - WhatsApp\nReference: WhatsApp conversation with Lav Kumar for full details\n\nRENTAL OPPORTUNITY:\n- Available: Tyre repair shop space (becomes vacant June 30)\n- NOT Available: Car wash, vacuum bay (ADNOC to operate)\n\nSTRATEGIC ASSESSMENT:\n- Good retail/residential location (vs. industrial sites)\n- Emarati Neighborhood- Limited rental scope (tyre shop only, other services ADNOC-operated)\n- ADNOC operational control limits ExpressFit service integration\n- **POSITIVE: ADNOC wants brand upgrade - WAG/ExpressFit positioning opportunity**\n- **POSITIVE: Clear timeline (June 30 availability)**\n- **CONSIDERATION: Rent expectation higher than 120K AED**\n\nRECOMMENDATION: MAYBE - Good location and demographics, ADNOC wants brand upgrade. Limited scope (tyre shop only) but clear opportunity window. Pursue if attractive terms and broader service rights can be negotiated. Timeline: Available June 30, 2026.",
    "recommendation": "MAYBE - Good location but limited rental scope (tyre shop only), ADNOC controls key services",
