    "assessment_notes": "In the middle of Abu Dhabi's industrial area (Mussafah). Surrounded by service shops, tire shops, and electrical shops. Location does not make sense for branded retail quick service. Heavy competition and industrial demographics.",
    "recommendation": "No Go - Industrial area, surrounded by competitors",
